The last option if none of the above two sparks any debate in your solution is to get rid of the anomalies. This is not recommended (as you\rquote re basically getting rid of some potentially valuable information) unless it\rquote s absolutely necessary and it doesn\rquote t harm the analysis in the future.\par
\par
